# Cursor workspace

- Project context: `.cursor/CLAUDE.md` (copy of `.claude/CLAUDE.md`).
- **Skills:** `.cursor/skills/<topic>/SKILL.md` — follow before that kind of work. They reference repo-root `_CONVENTIONS/...`; an identical tree also exists at `.cursor/_CONVENTIONS/` (keep both in sync if you edit conventions).
- **Agents:** `.cursor/agents/*.md`
- **Rules (from Claude Code):** `.cursor/rules-claude/*.md`
- **Scripts:** `.cursor/scripts/`

Do not rely on editing `.claude/` for Cursor; use this `.cursor/` tree. Originals remain under `.claude/` and `_CONVENTIONS/` for anyone still on Claude Code.

